-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

									STS
									---

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* assume-role-with-web-identity is an API provided by STS(Security Token Service)

* Returns temprorary security credential for users authnticated by a mobile or web id provider like amazon,facebook,google,etc

* For mobile application,Cognito is recommended

* Regular web application can use the STS assume-role-with-web-identity API

